Hello hello fellows! 

 

After 10  years of playing and modding the modders mod in the shadow for friends, ive finally decide to join tha community!

As me, my coding skill are a little outdated but still under dev and fixing, but thanks to you and this game i've learn so much in physics, dev and unity

I almost know some of you, so much I have read you, so much I have followed your work and delved into your line of code.

so in the hope of learning more, and of, who knows, maybe participating in some of your projects, I come to you brothers and sister

3 hours ago, Dr.Grym said:

Hello hello fellows!

"What's up doc? "  Welcome to the party.

10 hours ago, Caerfinon said:

"What's up doc? "  Welcome to the party. 

Thank you my dear sir,

And ahw, you know , fixing Kerbals patching codes, or it is the opposite?

Anyway! I could not resist and check your work and achievements, seeing your into Subs stuff too, good , good!

I was justly looking for parts of a submarine, so the universe seems to have heard my thoughts, rightey?

Next to that, i've started translating few add-on to Dutch & some French during freetime and orbital transfer, must stay in the move, warmey in the deep cold space ya know.
Top of the spaceship to you, dear sirs!
